title: CWTK - Love Yums / Kärleksmums - Chocolate Cake

media:group.media:title: CWTK - Love Yums / Kärleksmums - Chocolate Cake
media:group.media:description:
Welcome back to more CWTK, got a cocolate craving? Look no further, this is so easy a niendertal can make it.

Preheat Oven to 175c
Start melting butter, keep a eye on it.
Whip Eggs and Sugar somewhat Fluffy
Add all dry ingridients and whip it some more.
Take butter off stove and use it to butter a pan.
Add Milk to the Butter to cool it down.
Add Milk/Butter to the rest of the ingredients and
whip some more. 
Pour into a pan and into the oven for 20-25minutes.
Poke it with a toothpick to check doneness.

While the cake is in the Oven, make glaze.
Melt more butter and just mash everything together to your liking.

Take out the cake and pour the glaze evenly over it and add coco or whatever the hell you want.

Done

Cake:
225g Butterr 
2dl Milk
5x Egg
4,5dl Sugar
3 teaspoons Baking powder
6dl Floor
1 overfilled tablespoon Vanilla Suger 
1,5dl Cocoa Powder
3 teaspoons of baking soda.

Glaze:
100g Butter 
Coffee of some sort or Instant Coffee.
1dl Cacao almost 
2 tablespoons Vanila suger 
LOTS OF FLOOR SUGAR or about 4-5DL
Coconut Flakes

Explosion Effect by Green Screen Fisher.
